name: Catalina Whales Index
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Project Info: We are Bridgesplit - an NFT liquidity platform on Solana. We have submitted and successfully listed over 20+ coins and love working with CG.

We also have a new protocol we are launching - Elixir which will encompass an even smoother and more robust protocol for solana liquidity. All of these listings will be under the Bridgesplit infrastructure but powered by the Elixir UI and UX.
